The paper discusses a method for quality management in data warehouse, which is a topic related to database management (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed method also involves the use of algorithms and techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR) to dynamically specify key papers in each research area. Therefore, these sub-categories are also likely to be relevant to the paper.
